reviews.text: If you stay in Harbour Plaza North Point Hotel and are passing by here in afternoon, it may be a good idea to have a tea time rest.  HKD33 for a bowl of roasted duck rice noodle + a cup of ice milk tea or coffee.  Like the crispy duck skin and the noodle soup which is tasty and not oily.  The environment is  peaceful and relaxing.
Quality bargain meals, English and Chinese. Easy to order. You can even use the Octopus card at the ordering screen. Pick up at the counter. Then sit! Please note, no diet versions of soft drinks.
chain food stores... was there for some afternoon high-tea bite. Seems that the sets were less attractive and competitive compared with those we could opt for when we were young.

Good place to have local food including breakfast. Easy to order. Speaks English. Standard HK price. Had glutinous rice and tea for HK33. Would come back if staying at the Harbour Plaza North point Hotel which is just across the road.
It food was actually quite good! Recommended.

reviews.text: 隔離貴少少嗰邊會更好味 😋
美心MX快餐店走的是高級化路線、好讓上班一族及職業婦女下班後帶着疲憊身躯、偷懶一下又想吃到住家飯感覺、餐单多元化還有可進步空間、一年四季要配合節令口味要時有娈化讓食客有多些選擇、不可墨守成規、盼望有曙光更上一層樓
